text: Karadygan () is a rural locality (a village) in Bikbausky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 20 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Isyangulovo, 5 km from Trushino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Karadygan
